Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "maloj" in different forms and positions:

1. *Maloj* deci treba puno pažnje. (Little children need a lot of attention.)
2. Sinoć sam bio na rođendanu *malog* Petra. (Last night I was at the birthday party of little Peter.)
3. Ova kuća je *maloj* udaljenosti od centra grada. (This house is at a short distance from the city center.)
4. Upravo sam dobila poruku od *male* sestre. (I just received a message from my younger sister.)
5. Da li si video *malu* macu u parku? (Did you see the little cat in the park?)
6. *Maloj* tvrđavi nedostaju kule. (The small fortress lacks towers.)
7. *Male* pare su takođe važne. (Small change is also important.)
8. Ovo je *malo* drugačiji pristup problemu. (This is a slightly different approach to the problem.)

I have highlighted the word "maloj" with a star. The translations in English are provided in parentheses.